message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present our premium product to you. This item holds significant value to me, but I understand its true worth to you is even greater. I am offering this exceptional product to you for $11,000. This price reflects a fair compromise considering both its intrinsic value and your appreciation for it. I believe this opportunity is not to be missed, and I look forward to discussing how this product could enhance your experience or business. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
